TASK

To install httpd 
To create user
To start the service 


Below is a playbook to execute the task

vim playbook1.yml


---
- hosts: all
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: install httpd
      yum:
        name: httpd
        state: present

    - name: start httpd
      service:
        name: httpd
        state: started

    - name: create user
      user:
        name: Ahmed
        state: present
~



:wq to save

 ansible-playbook playbook.yml

ansible all -a "httpd -version" -b

ansible all -a "systemctl status httpd" -b


